  <breakfast><![CDATA[<p>A freshly prepared buffet breakfast is served each day and includes delicious organic produce such as yogurts, jams, pastries breads, fruits, meats, cheeses and fresh naturally pressed juices. Hot dishes are available and are made to order. Breakfast is served from 7.00am - 11.00am from Mon - Sat and 7.00am - 12.00pm on Sunday. </p>]]></breakfast>
